<h2>Where to Start?</h2>

<ol class="steps-list">
  <li><span class="step-num">01</span><div><strong>Analysis — How many channels are you receiving reservations from?</strong> Measure the update time in each channel. The point with the highest double-booking risk is your starting point.</div></li>
  <li><span class="step-num">02</span><div><strong>Prioritization — Start with the guest communication flow.</strong> Confirmation, reminder, and check-in information — these three go into a single automation flow and provide immediately visible impact.</div></li>
  <li><span class="step-num">03</span><div><strong>Implementation — Make your PMS or channel manager the center.</strong> Automation flows can be set up with Beds24, Cloudbeds, or Channel Manager integration.</div></li>
